overview: While Bobby fills his stable of working girls (including notable starlets Amber Rayne, Gabriella Banks, and Melissa Martinez), his search for the hottest hookers leads him to LA's most notorious underground sex club.  In the Hollywood Hills, Tracy (Diana Espen) and Jake play a little game for the heart and body of young and innocent Brittney (Allysin Chaynes). But when Brittney's husband proves he's the man of the hour, Jake Andre will either have to settle for his stripper wife (Alana Evans) or find a new object of obsession.
title: Dirty Angels 4: Object of Obsession
